            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> into quarters</p><p>Cut your<strong> cucumber</strong> into quarters lengthways, then slice finely</p><p>Chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them finely, discard the stems</p><p>Cut your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> in half</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1580806779084-x200.jpg",
