      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>juice</strong> of the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> with your <strong>natural yoghurt</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> – this is your<strong> lemon yoghurt</strong></p>",
